text: Itumbiara subdilatata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1872. It is known from Nicaragua, Costa Rica and Panama.BioLib.cz - Itumbiara subdilatata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1872
